<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Mermaid Diagrams</h1>
</div>

<p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 24px;">
  service-mermaid provides a Ruby DSL for building Mermaid diagrams with server-side SVG rendering.
</p>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Flowchart</h2>
  <p>A sample flowchart built with the <code>build_flowchart</code> controller helper, demonstrating nodes, links, and shapes.</p>
  <%= link_to "View Flowchart", diagrams_flowchart_path, class: "btn" %>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <h2>Sequence Diagram</h2>
  <p>A sample sequence diagram built with the <code>build_sequence_diagram</code> helper, showing the request lifecycle.</p>
  <%= link_to "View Sequence Diagram", diagrams_sequence_path, class: "btn" %>
</div>
